title: Support + Jungler Needed (Bronze)
body:
Hi guys,

Looking for  support and jungle mains for a Bronze based team. Just because we're bronze doesn't mean that we're not looking to improve and progress through elos. You'd need to be available for practice sessions when messaged and team meetings. Contact via Skype is preferable however not necessary. We like to pride ourselves on trying to be as non toxic as possible while maintaining good communication even when the situation is not looking great as we're still learning.

If anyone has any suggestions for a good ranked 5's coach please let me know as this would also be appreciated.

Thanks once again,

Jollzstar
